general.desc: Otsuka Information Technology Corp is a Taiwan-based company engaged in designing, trading, maintaining, importing, and exporting hardware, software, computers, network and accessories. Its major products generating revenues are CAD, Subscription contracts, Services, 3D animation, Game engines, and others. It earns maximum revenues from software sales.
general.short_desc: Otsuka Information Technology Corp designs & markets three-dimensional computer software. It produces computer aided industrial design, computer aided design, computer aided manufacturing, computer aided engineering, and document management software.
